  "text": "The purpose of this study was to apply 2005 ATS/ERS and [CITATION_1] guidelines along with our own criteria to determine pulmonary function patterns in ten patients who underwent simple spirometry following high concentration of chlorine gas inhalation after a train derailment in Graniteville, South Carolina.",
